::KitKat::

She emerged from the CR chamber and walked to her room.  She closed 
the door behind her but didn't lock it.  She layed down on her bed 
and put her arm up over her eyes.  She was slowly starting to fall 
asleep.  She opened her eyes and sat up.  She thought about what had 
happened.  She was mad at herself for letting her anger and her honor 
take control when she shouldhave been thinking.  She sighed and knew 
what she had to do.  She got up and walked to the main room and knelt 
down on one knee infront of Megatron.  She lowered her head and 
waited for the blow to come.
